sub_title: AVS Catalog Associate at Amazon | International Relations | Cross-Cultural Communication | Project Management
summary:
Experienced and dedicated Catalog Associate with a strong background in process development and data analysis. I possess a deep understanding of effective cross-cultural communication strategies and thrive in diverse and global environments. With a commitment to a detail-oriented approach, I excel at ensuring accurate and high-quality digital content.

Throughout my experience as a Catalog Associate at Amazon, I have consistently performed quality checks on digital content, meticulously validating errors to ensure the highest level of accuracy and consistency. Working in English and Swedish, I have effectively communicated with professionals from diverse backgrounds, fostering strong relationships and driving successful collaborations.

With a Master of Arts degree in Language and Communication Coaching, I possess advanced skills in developing and implementing effective communication strategies across international contexts. My Bachelor‘s degree in International Business Communication has provided me with a solid foundation in understanding the intricacies of global market dynamics and navigating cultural nuances.

Passionate about cultural diversity and following emerging communication trends, I continuously seek opportunities to expand my skillset and implement innovative approaches to achieve effective international communication.
